  name: "Lucky Glitch"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "Starting at 4th level, whenever a scavenger triggers a glitch when\
    \ using a timeworn technological item, she rolls twice and can choose which of\
    \ the two glitch effects actually occurs. A scavenger always adds her level to\
    \ rolls to determine what kind of glitch occurs, and treats rolls of over 100\
    \ as 100."
  effects: null
